  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Children with acute otitis media

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Amoxicillin allergy

          -  Tympanic membrane perforation

          -  Tympanostomy tubes (current)

          -  Complication of acute otitis media such as mastoiditis
      </textblock>
